                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "BudgetGroupID",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " of 0 might not be expected by all consumers of this procedure, potentially leading to confusion or errors if not documented."
